title: #744 - Jesus Trejo
description:
Jesus Trejo, a comedian and actor seen on Netflix' "Mr. Iglesias," joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio.

Look for Jesus' debut comedy special on SHOWTIME; and his show on Complex, "Taco's con Todo" in early 2020. 

This podcast is brought to you by:

Behind The Irishman podcast - Go behind the scenes with host Sebastian Maniscalco and learn about Martin Scorsese's new Netflix movie "The Irishman." http://smarturl.it/behindtheirishman
